1995/08/08:SK & TI
Additional subroutines for GRACE systems.
1. bshbok, sphbok.
   conversion from BASES/SPRING histograms
              to   HBOOK.

   The relation of ID in BASES/SPRING to ID for HBOOK.

   ID for HBOOK = ID in BASES/SPRING + (OFFSET)

  ----------------------------------------
                         BASES     SPRING
   Histogram   (1-D)         0      20000
   Scatter Plot(2-D)     10000      30000
  ----------------------------------------
2. bsgetw, bsputw
   Weight
